title: AI song generator Udio offers brief window for downloads after Universal settlement upsets users
description: AI song generation platform Udio said it would give its frustrated users 48 hours to download their songs before the company shifts to a new business model to comply with a legal settlement.

title: Ashland High School to host senior dinner, concert

title: Sabalenka serves her way past Paolini at WTA Finals; Gauff hits 17 double-faults in loss to Pegula
description: RIYADH, Saudi Arabia (AP) — Top-ranked Aryna Sabalenka put on a dominant serving display in her opening match at the WTA finals, producing 10 aces in a 6-3, 6-1 win over No. 8-ranked Jasmine Paolini on Sunday.
